cards.rulesText:
{Blocker}
This Unit has +2 power while fighting a Legend.
When a Rival adjusts or swaps 1 or more friendly Gigs, you may add a card from your trash to your hand.

{Go Solo}
{Attack} Reveal the top card of your deck and add it to your hand. This Unit gains power equal to that card's cost this turn.
{Defeated} A Rival discards 1.
